highlights.text: “Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 272 weeks straight.
“Flowers” by Lauren Spencer-Smith is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #72.
The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Blinding Lights” is the highest at #29.
“Payphone” by Maroon 5 and Wiz Khalifa is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 43 spots at #70.
